label truck_kunDate:
    scene bg black
    show textBeach
    scene bg beach

    "Truck-kun is sitting silently on the sand, watching the sun paint the sea orange, as Protagonist-kun approaches him."

    show protagonist mask at right
    mc "So. What are you?"

    show truck_kun suspicious at left
    bm "Hm? Whatever could you mean?"

    show protagonist mask angry at right
    mc "You're weird. You weren't a monster like the girls were, you were a car. And you somehow managed to travel to my world."

    show truck_kun smug at left
    bm "Your world, my world, this world, what difference does it make? It's all fake anyway."

    show protagonist mask at right
    mc "Fake?"

    show truck_kun surprised at left
    bm "Yes. Fake. Not real. A story that someone is telling."

    show protagonist mask surprised at right
    mc "You're not making any sense."

    show truck_kun smug at left
    bm "Perhaps."

    show truck_kun smug at left
    bm "But what does that matter? People had fun making this little game that we're in. I'd say that's the true gift of this little world we're currently in."

    show protagonist mask at right
    mc "Are you talking about the Town Mayor's Selection? That game?"

    show truck_kun happy at left
    bm "Ah, no. You're not ready for the truth yet."

    "The two of them sit still and listen to the waves."

    show truck_kun happy at left
    bm "Why did you ask me to come here? You could've gone on a date with one of the girls."

    show truck_kun happy at left
    bm "Is it because the game's entire non-existent budget went to me and now I look way hotter than anyone else in this game?"

    show protagonist mask surprised at right
    mc "What budget?"

    show truck_kun happy at left
    bm "You're right. This is a jam game. The budget was zero."

    show protagonist mask angry at right
    mc "I don't understand you. At all. It's like everything you say brings up seven more questions."

    show truck_kun happy at left 
    bm "Maybe I'm talking to the player instead of you."

    show protagonist mask angry at right
    mc "You're doing that thing again! Stop it!"

    "Truck-kun goes to leave."

    show protagonist mask angry at right
    mc "Where are you going? I still have questions?!"

    show truck_kun smug at left 
    bm "I have a job to do."

    show protagonist mask surprised at right
    mc "What job?"

    show truck_kun smug at left 
    bm "Well..."

    show truck_kun happy at left
    bm "Someone has to transport the protagonists to new worlds."

    show protagonist angry at right 
    mc "I'm giving up. You're incapable of making any sense."

    show truck_kun smug at left
    bm "See ya."
    return